Package: Smoothseg
Type: Package
Title: Generating and Plotting Multiple Changepoint Predictions
Version: 0.1.4
Author: Oliver Li
Maintainer: Oliver Li <oli.li@alumni.unc.edu>
Description: Smoothseg is a package with functions for generating interactive plotly objects for changepoint predictions.
    It can accommodate irregularly spaced data as well as timeseries.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
